            <para>
                <emph type="bold">Switch Installation</emph>
            </para>
            <para>Refer to the Figure below.</para>
            <para>If there is available switch capacity in Location One, install the fog light control switch in
                Location one. If the Location One switch pack module is fully populated, install a six pack (p/n
                3549776C4) in Location Two. Additional switch blanks (p/n 3533950C1) may be needed to cover unused
                switch locations.
            </para>
            <figure id="f7300065" figsize="pg-wide">
